text: Iosif Culineac was a water polo player from Romania. Culineac competed at the 1964 Summer Olympics and the 1972 Summer Olympics. He was born on 13 August 1941 and died on 26 July 2022.Iosif Culineac == References == Category:1941 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Romanian water polo players Category:Olympians for Romania Category:Sportspeople from Bucharest
